[*] WaitingForSale --> AddingItems : new sale
AddingItems --> PaymentProcessing : all items added
PaymentProcessing --> CashPaymentApproved : cash payment
PaymentProcessing --> CardOrCheckPaymentPending : card or check
CashPaymentApproved --> SaleCompleted : payment approved
CardOrCheckPaymentPending --> SaleCompleted : payment approved
SaleCompleted --> WaitingForSale : next customer

